## Overview

Led UX design for FEMA GO platform modernization, evolving an inherited USWDS-based design system into a scalable, governed system supporting complex grant workflows.

---

## Key Contributions

- Standardized form components  
- Defined alert and status patterns  
- Established button hierarchy  
- Built consistent layouts and grids  
- Improved modal workflows  

---

## Notes

This repository supports the live portfolio page and includes artifacts used in the case study.
